=== Historic site ===
* {{jalink|Kamo Site (Kawanishi)|Q18701075|Kamo Site}} (National {{jalink|Historic Site|Q1081138}}, designated July 31, 2000)
: Settlement remains from the {{jalink|Paleolithic|Q11768}} and {{jalink|Jōmon period|Q52824}} through the {{jalink|Heian period|Q193292}}. Excavated artifacts are displayed at the Kawanishi City Cultural Properties Museum.

=== Transportation ===
